<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">Connect an extra monitor</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="p">To set up a second monitor with your desktop computer, connect the monitor.
     If your system doesn't recognize it immediately, or you would like to adjust
     the settings:
  </p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click your name on the menu bar and select <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.
  </p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Abra <span class="gui">Pantalles</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Calque na imaxe del monitor que quier activar o desactivar, y arrastre l'eslizador escontra <span class="gui">❙/○</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">The monitor with the <span class="link"><a href="unity-menubar-intro.html" title="Xestione aplicaciones y configuraciones cola barra de menús">menu bar</a></span> is the main monitor. To change which monitor is
           "main", click on the top bar and drag it over to the monitor you want to set as
           the "main" monitor.
  </p></li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">Pa camudar la posición» d'un monitor, calque nél y arrastre a la posición deseada.</p>
<div class="note" title="Nota"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">Si quier que dambos monitores amuesen el mesmu conteníu, active'l caxellu <span class="gui">Espeyar pantalles</span>.</p></div></div></div></div>
</li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Cuando configure too al so gustu, calque <span class="gui">Aplicar</span> y dempués <span class="gui">Caltener esta configuración</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">To close the <span class="gui">Displays</span> click on the <span class="gui">x</span> in the top
           corner.
  </p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
</div>
